<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦٢١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6106">مُسْلِمُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6685">هِشَامٌ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">وَشُعْبَةُ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيَّبِ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«الْعَائِدُ فِي هِبَتِهِ كَالْعَائِدِ فِي قَيْئِهِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>